etz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/former-israeli-finance-minister-avraham-shochat-dies-at-87/0000018d-f14b-d401-a3dd-f95b811d0000</link><description>这位工党政客曾担任阿拉德市市长 22 年，并担任议会议员 14 年。肖查特与伊扎克·拉宾关系密切，负责《奥斯陆协议》的经济方面</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 20:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/former-israeli-finance-minister-avraham-shochat-dies-at-87/0000018d-f14b-d401-a3dd-f95b811d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>